''See also [[han]]''
==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|hä}}

===Personal pronoun===
'''hän''' (''stems'' '''häne-''' ''and'' '''hän-''')
#[[he]] or [[she]] (''of a [[human being]]'')

====Declension====
The [[consonant stem]] '''hän-''' is found only in the [[partitive]], otherwise the [[vowel stem]] '''häne-''' is used. Case suffixes are regular. The [[comitative]] and [[instructive]] forms don't exist; the [[abessive]] is hardly used.

